{"tid":1932800,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（係唔係在囚手足俾人打？）懲教人員制止還押在囚人士打鬥","createTime":"2020-03-19T02:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T05:42:24.000Z","uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8a94f6fdee69f6e97707f1a5fd3c056e5bbbc3","tid":1932800,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"懲教人員制止還押在囚人士打鬥<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　荔枝角收押所懲教人員今日（三月十八日）制止還押在囚人士打鬥。<br />\n<br />\n　　今日上午七時五十二分，兩名年齡分別<span style=\"color: red;\">三十歲</span>及四十三歲男性還押在囚人士在前往日間活動室期間發生打鬥。在場懲教人員見狀立即上前制止，並召喚支援人員到場。<br />\n<br />\n　　事件中，一名還押在囚人士頭部及胸部受傷，需送往公立醫院作進一步診治。另一名還押在囚人士手部及頸部受傷，經院所醫生治理後無需送院。<br />\n<br />\n　　有關事件已轉交警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n　　兩名還押在囚人士分別因<span style=\"color: red;\">無牌管有槍械或彈藥罪</span>及盜竊罪而被還押。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年3月18日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間20時02分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/18/P2020031800773.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F18%2FP2020031800773.htm&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=78c56789\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/18/P2020031800773.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">上年11月有手足被還押至今</span><br />\n<br />\n警方日前在記者會上透露，曾派員假扮買家，成功拘捕一名涉嫌在網上出售武器的男子，行動中檢獲12支電槍及26支伸縮棍。案件今早在九龍城裁判法院提訊，被告暫時毋須答辯，等候警方進一步調查，案件押後至12月16日再訊。據悉，警方於被告手機內發現針對警方言論，調查期間發現有50多人曾於被告的facebook內留言，表示有興趣購買武器，暫未知購買武器是否與近月示威活動有關。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】旺角無限復活抗「撕」暴 義工：文宣是最低成本抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被告趙梓烽（30歲）被控無牌經營槍械、管有違禁武器及無牌管有槍械</span>等四罪，涉於今年11月1日在大坑東邨遊樂場及旺角一間遊戲機中心的儲物室內，沒有相關牌照下經營及管有共12支電槍及26支伸縮棍。<br />\n<br />\n控方指案件可能轉往較高級別的法院處理，基於案情嚴重及證據強烈，反對被告保釋。裁判官最終拒絕被告保釋申請，被告其間須還柙。<br />\n【案件編號：KCCC2663/19】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191104/QFTPMLWV6CLIKVT6X2C73PAVNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FQFTPMLWV6CLIKVT6X2C73PAVNA%2F&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=a3114dce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FQFTPMLWV6CLIKVT6X2C73PAVNA%2F&h=9081428b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191104/QFTPMLWV6CLIKVT6X2C73PAVNA/</a>"},{"pid":"8105714dfa54cb9c4390642930d3e32e8b910f68","tid":1932800,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2af2ba76899c5a51fbbbdb43f49ee0e22f59083","tid":1932800,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c080044dcb271c9c75fc4f0dc967b7d082b40d4d","tid":1932800,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"死監躉就最麻煩 坐監都仲搞搞陣"},{"pid":"9310222fb589eb5b1f2811c894806cec744c522a","tid":1932800,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c080044dcb271c9c75fc4f0dc967b7d082b40d4d","tid":1932800,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"死監躉就最麻煩 坐監都仲搞搞陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收押人士啊"},{"pid":"0036e3d333713a6dd72dbb00695d0e497f001c1c","tid":1932800,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=